high_descs: Turn left then head right then turn to face the stove on your left.
Pick up the kettle that is on the upper right-hand corner of the stove top.
Turn around then head left towards the sink.
Place the kettle into the sink and rinse it off then pick it back up.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Put the kettle down on the upper right-hand corner of the stove top.
anns.task_desc: Take the Kettle from the stove, wash it and put it back.

high_descs: walk through kitchen to face stove
pick up kettle from stove right back burner
wash kettle in sink, pick up kettle from sink
place kettle on stove back right burner
anns.task_desc: put a washed kettle onto a stove top

high_descs: Take a step forward then turn left and walk past the counter to your right then turn right and walk to the stove turning left to face it and walking towards it when you get there.
Pick up the tea pot on the back right burner that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the sink then take a step to your right.
Fill the tea pot with water in the sink then shut off the tap.
Walk back to where you got the tea pot.
Put the tea pot back on the back right burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a full tea pot on the burner.
